  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.6.7">
<l>muṭiyāta teṉṉeṉak kēliṉi muḻuvē ḻulaku muṇṭā ṉukantuvan</l>
<l>tuṭiyēṉuḷ pukuntā ṉakalvāṉu mallaṉiṉi</l>
<l>ceṭiyār nōyka ḷellān turantemar kīḻmē lēḻpiṟappum</l>
<l>viṭiyā vennarakat teṉṟuñ cērttaṉ māṟiṉarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What will be impossible to me? If so,  the one who swallowed all the seven worlds joyfully came</l>
<l>[and] entered the heart of me, his servant, and he will not leave now.</l>
<l>Abandoning all pains full of evil  my people through seven birth before [and] after</l>
<l>have been changed from forever joining endless  hot hell.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
